{"tid":2328204,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"韓國女團第一次！GFRIEND 接受葛萊美博物館專訪，分享成功要訣與近期計畫","createTime":"2020-12-16T11:50:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-18T14:50:56.000Z","uid":16659,"like":12,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"3a433053a97b2b297ac0cb896a5f9af88e1f851d","tid":2328204,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T11:50:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_6e055940131065e7fc47a00b40be9c97/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-12-16/132364-889152.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_6e055940131065e7fc47a00b40be9c97%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-12-16%2F132364-889152.png&h=11457412&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nGFRIEND 今年連續三次以令人驚豔的作品開創新風格，迅速在海外引發關注之餘，也成為第一組獲邀登上 &ldquo;Mini Masterclass&rdquo; 的韓國女團！<br />\n<br />\n葛萊美博物館最近邀請 GFRIEND 參加 Mini Masterclass，與她們嚴肅地聊聊與音樂有關的話題，並於 15 日公開了專訪影片。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pQlXZgcUQyI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DpQlXZgcUQyI&d=c%2B6PkbrQ5MzYtHY5m9tE13Kg77Sy3LnB9Oyli8DN%2Bms%3D&h=0e07dc54\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pQlXZgcUQyI</a><br />\n訪談從專業角度切入，首先問 GFRIEND 的是「如果想在妳們的工作上成功，需要哪些技能和特質？」，GFRIEND 紛紛提出實力、有別於他人的鮮明特色等等；談及身為藝人的最大優點時，GFRIEND 則認為是「可以讓粉絲看見各式各樣的作品」，還有「獲得五個像家人一樣可靠的隊友」。<br />\n<br />\n特別的是，GFRIEND 在訪談中也提及由於年末將至，正在準備精彩的表演，還透露：「如果有好機會，希望每個成員都能用一首新歌組成一張新專輯，感覺應該會滿不錯的。」很期待這一天的到來啊！"},{"pid":"5fec6c84cdbbc3c690e4f8a2a7d8c6299b10d0d9","tid":2328204,"uid":93096,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T11:51:06.000Z","msg":"好似好勁咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97ecc1cab7251a1f038774a0b0213c2b33f75a79","tid":2328204,"uid":33410,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T11:52:29.000Z","msg":"續約未"},{"pid":"caae8eeea9e420fc3a680106de1ac281db4720c4","tid":2328204,"uid":165368,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score"